      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/aguti00/{size}/675_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-01-24T13:30:33.332Z",
      "cooked": "<p>You can limit the daily training time here.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05_2_690x400.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"vFvbPIcJagKRyWvRUzOBC3xLYMZ\" width=\"690\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05_2_690x400.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/ddf46bd09e1bb328196991fb86e35a7eebd2cd05_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">995\u00d7577 31.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>And if you want more intensity in that time, go up with the intensity ramp. Keep in mind that certain workouts have a minimum time, that is, there are workouts of 1h:15m, and these will not reduce your time no matter how much you put 1h on the limit.</p>",
